    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I like the decentralized aspect of the second proposal. And even though it's gonna be another method to implement, it's not mandatory if you don't plan to remove the widget so we can still hack / prototype widget. Also it makes for a more explicit API.\r\n\r\nI have some questions:\r\n - do you have something planned to lower the number of search calls in case of multiple remove?\r\n - do you have an idea for the dynamic `addWidget`?",
